<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">والعافية:</span> أَوْ أَرادَنِي بِرَحْمَةٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">والمودة:</span> رَأْفَةً وَرَحْمَةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والسعة:</span> تَخْفِيفٌ مِنْ رَبِّكُمْ وَرَحْمَةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والمغفرة:</span> كَتَبَ عَلى نَفْسِهِ الرَّحْمَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والعصمة:</span> لا عاصِمَ الْيَوْمَ مِنْ أَمْرِ اللَّهِ إِلَّا مَنْ رَحِمَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ومن ذلك:</span> الفتنة: وردت على أوجه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الشرك:</span> وَالْفِتْنَةُ أَشَدُّ مِنَ الْقَتْلِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والإضلال:</span> ابْتِغاءَ الْفِتْنَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والقتل:</span> أَنْ يَفْتِنَكُمُ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والصدّ:</span> وَاحْذَرْهُمْ أَنْ يَفْتِنُوكَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">والضلالة:</span> وَمَنْ يُرِدِ اللَّهُ فِتْنَتَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والمعذرة:</span> ثُمَّ لَمْ تَكُنْ فِتْنَتُهُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والقضاء:</span> إِنْ هِيَ إِلَّا فِتْنَتُكَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والإثم:</span> أَلا فِي الْفِتْنَةِ سَقَطُوا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">والمرض:</span> يُفْتَنُونَ فِي كُلِّ عامٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">والعبرة:</span> لا تَجْعَلْنا فِتْنَةً.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">والعقوبة:</span> أَنْ تُصِيبَهُمْ فِتْنَةٌ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">والاختبار:</span> وَلَقَدْ فَتَنَّا الَّذِينَ مِنْ قَبْلِهِمْ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">والعذاب:</span> جَعَلَ فِتْنَةَ النَّاسِ كَعَذابِ اللَّهِ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">والإحراق:</span> يَوْمَ هُمْ عَلَى النَّارِ يُفْتَنُونَ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">والجنون:</span> بِأَيِّكُمُ الْمَفْتُونُ.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">ومن ذلك:</span> الروح،<span class="c5"> ورد على أوجه:</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>